  "description": "A vibrant nighttime scene showcases a spectacular fireworks display over a city skyline and iconic bridges. The fireworks explode in a brilliant array of red, white, and gold, creating a large, dazzling bloom in the sky. Below, the city is a tapestry of illuminated buildings, with the Bay Bridge and the Golden Gate Bridge clearly visible. The bridges are lit up with strings of lights, adding to the festive atmosphere. Dark water stretches out in the foreground, reflecting some of the lights. The overall effect is dramatic and celebratory.",
